---
import mapsvg from './map.svg?raw'
---

<div class='mx-auto mt-40 max-w-5xl p-5'>
    <h2 class='my-5 text-center text-2xl'>
        <i class='bi bi-geo-fill'></i> Traveling the world
    </h2>
    <hr class='mx-auto h-1 w-3/4 rounded border-0 bg-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-200' />

    <p class='my-5 text-center'>
        I dream of exploring and visiting as many countries as possible, living in different countries throughout my life. Luckily, in tech industry we have the
        ability to work remotely from where we want thanks to bleisure. What an amazing oportunity!
    </p>

    <Fragment set:html={mapsvg} />
</div>
